---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Poetry Corner">
  <Navbar />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
      >
        About Me
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        The story behind the poetry
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- macOS window wrapper -->
      <div
        class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200/60 dark:border-gray-700/60"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-gray-200/60 dark:border-gray-700/60 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-md"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mx-auto text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            About
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div
              class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16"
            >
              <div>
                <h2
                  class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
                >
                  नमस्ते! मैं अवनीश हूँ
                </h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    This space is a small corner of my heart where I share my
                    poetry and thoughts. Every poem I write carries a piece of
                    my mind and soul.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    My journey into poetry started quite unexpectedly when I was
                    in class 8 or 9. It was a winter night, and my grandfather
                    had come to our place. He was snuggled in a quilt, sitting
                    back straight, not sleeping, just lost in his own calm. I
                    don't know how it happened, but something magical took over
                    me that night. I had never really studied poetry, though I
                    always liked it.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    That day, my father had given me a new diary. I opened it,
                    took my pen, and without thinking much, wrote the word
                    "अक्षर (Akshar)" at the top of the page. Then words started
                    flowing on their own. I didn't plan the poem. It just
                    happened.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    When I finished, I read it to my grandfather. He smiled
                    gently, that typical Indian elder's smile that hides so many
                    emotions, and simply said, "Badhiya hai, Likhna hi chahiye!"
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    I don't force myself to write. It just happens. Whenever I
                    feel something deeply, it finds its way into words. And when
                    I'm not writing, usually exploring nature, or quietly
                    observing people and places around me.
                  </p>
                  <p
                    class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium italic"
                  >
                    Poetry is not something I do. It's something that happens to
                    me.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative">
                <div
                  class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
                  <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div
                      class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-4 border-white/30 shadow-2xl"
                    >
                      <img
                        src="/me.jpeg"
                        alt="Avanish"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Writing Journey</h3>
                    <p class="opacity-90">
                      From that winter night with my grandfather to today, every
                      word carries a piece of my heart.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Section -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
                Let's Connect
              </h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
                I'd love to hear your thoughts on my poetry or share in
                meaningful conversations about life, art, and everything in
                between.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a
                  href="mailto:avanishpandey511@gmail.com"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                  Get in Touch
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://instagram.com/avanish._._"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                  Connect on Instagram
                </a>
                <a
                  href="/poems"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105"
                >
                  Read My Poems
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 py-12 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Avanish's Corner
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Where words dance with emotions
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
            >Home</a
          >
          <a
            href="/poems"
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
            >Poems</a
          >
          <a
            href="/memories"
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
            >Memories</a
          >
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
            >About</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pt-8">
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
          © 2025 Avanish. Made with ❤️ and poetry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
